name: CC_calibration_date
notes: sensor calibration date (milliseconds since 1970-01-01). This timestamp is the factory calibration date which does not match the filename date which is the start of a glider deployment where the salinity setting was changed.

name: CC_ref_salinity
notes: Optode salinity setting. This file was created as an intermediate file when a glider deployment updated the salinity setting to 0.
